name: Parnaviii
greetingText: I love youuu so so fucking much!!!
wishText: Babe this is my first valentines proposal and it feels like i always wanted to have this with you. When i look at the all the time we spent, the memories we made, the laughs we had, the kisses we had and the future i have thought of us, I do so with the smile on my face. You are something so beautiful that God saw and decided to let me have it.So here it goes my babyGurlll, would you like to be my first and only valentine ?
